(GRUNTING)

1296
01:13:38.458 --> 01:13:41.083
I really was just trying
to knock you out. I wasn't...

1297
01:13:41.917 --> 01:13:43.792
I swear to God. you know...

1298
01:13:44.750 --> 01:13:45.999
I wasn't trying to...

1299
01:13:46.000 --> 01:13:47.749
- LINDA: Just stop.
- It was just...

1300
01:13:47.750 --> 01:13:50.916
You don't have to keep
saying that. I-I believe you.

1301
01:13:50.917 --> 01:13:51.917
Mmm.

1302
01:13:53.375 --> 01:13:54.708
LINDA: (EXHALES)

1303
01:13:55.833 --> 01:13:56.708
(SOBS)

1304
01:13:59.167 --> 01:14:02.000
LINDA: I tasted something
bitter. but I just... (SCOFFS)

1305
01:14:03.042 --> 01:14:04.416
I really didn't want to think

1306
01:14:04.417 --> 01:14:06.000
you could
do something like that.

1307
01:14:07.042 --> 01:14:07.917
But...

1308
01:14:09.375 --> 01:14:10.499
Anyway. you know what.

1309
01:14:10.500 --> 01:14:12.791
it would take a hell of a lot
more berries than that to...

1310
01:14:12.792 --> 01:14:14.125
kill a human being.

1311
01:14:14.667 --> 01:14:15.500
Yeah.

1312
01:14:15.792 --> 01:14:16.707
LINDA: For next time.

1313
01:14:16.708 --> 01:14:19.791
I even screwed that up.
(CHUCKLES)

1314
01:14:19.792 --> 01:14:20.999
Such an idiot.

1315
01:14:21.000 --> 01:14:23.750
- BRADLEY: (CRYING)
- (SHUSHING)

1316
01:14:26.667 --> 01:14:27.583
It's okay.

1317
01:14:27.958 --> 01:14:29.541
- I get it.
- (SOBS)

1318
01:14:29.542 --> 01:14:31.167
Here. here. here.

1319
01:14:31.708 --> 01:14:33.875
Come on. let's get
your strength back. huh?

1320
01:14:34.792 --> 01:14:35.708
Again.

1321
01:14:36.333 --> 01:14:37.250
(WHIMPERING) Okay.

1322
01:14:39.292 --> 01:14:40.750
- There you go.
- Mmm.

1323
01:14:41.167 --> 01:14:42.000
Yeah.

1324
01:14:43.042 --> 01:14:44.375
(SIGHS)

1325
01:14:44.917 --> 01:14:48.375
Now. some things are gonna
have to change with you.

1326
01:14:49.292 --> 01:14:51.666
- And it's not gonna be easy.
- Definitely.

1327
01:14:51.667 --> 01:14:52.958
Yeah.

1328
01:14:53.750 --> 01:14:56.374
(GROANS)
I've really been thinking

1329
01:14:56.375 --> 01:14:58.625
how I can get through to you.

1330
01:14:59.208 --> 01:15:01.332
Do you want some?
You haven't eaten.

1331
01:15:01.333 --> 01:15:02.666
I'm okay. thanks.

1332
01:15:02.667 --> 01:15:04.125
- You sure?
- Yeah.

1333
01:15:04.583 --> 01:15:06.042
Still have a queasy tummy.

1334
01:15:07.042 --> 01:15:08.042
Right.

1335
01:15:09.500 --> 01:15:10.624
- I know how hard...
- So stupid.

1336
01:15:10.625 --> 01:15:12.000
...this all must be for you.

1337
01:15:13.250 --> 01:15:15.042
Not being in control.

1338
01:15:15.792 --> 01:15:17.707
- Ahh.
- You're not used to...

1339
01:15:17.708 --> 01:15:19.917
- (CLICKING TONGUE)
- being in this. shall we say.

1340
01:15:20.958 --> 01:15:22.707
...submissive position.

1341
01:15:22.708 --> 01:15:24.707
(CLICKING TONGUE)

1342
01:15:24.708 --> 01:15:25.707
I mean. it's natural

1343
01:15:25.708 --> 01:15:27.499
for you not to be able
to take orders from me.

1344
01:15:27.500 --> 01:15:31.124
To have to depend on me
for your survival.

1345
01:15:31.125 --> 01:15:32.542
- You know?
- (WHEEZES)

1346
01:15:33.292 --> 01:15:34.250
It's just natural.

1347
01:15:34.917 --> 01:15:36.916
You're a slave to your biology.

1348
01:15:36.917 --> 01:15:39.000
- (GURGLE)
- Oh!

1349
01:15:40.125 --> 01:15:41.917
Feeling kinda funny. huh?

1350
01:15:42.708 --> 01:15:44.292
- Can't move?
- (WHEEZES)

1351
01:15:44.792 --> 01:15:48.542
That's the neurotoxins
from this blue-ringed octopus.

1352
01:15:49.750 --> 01:15:53.417
Blocks the transmission
of nerve impulses.

1353
01:15:54.875 --> 01:15:56.500
Caught it about a week ago.

1354
01:15:57.500 --> 01:16:00.500
Was really hoping I wouldn't
have to use it. but...

1355
01:16:01.125 --> 01:16:02.500
...held on to it.

1356
01:16:03.750 --> 01:16:05.083
Just in case.

1357
01:16:07.125 --> 01:16:08.624
(SIGHS)

1358
01:16:08.625 --> 01:16:11.666
Now. you did a great job
with that raft. I gotta say.

1359
01:16:11.667 --> 01:16:13.125
You really are a quick study.

1360
01:16:14.542 --> 01:16:17.042
But if you really wanted it
to hold...

1361
01:16:17.333 --> 01:16:18.457
(SLURS INDISTINCTLY)

1362
01:16:18.458 --> 01:16:21.917
...you should have used
double floor lashing.

1363
01:16:23.250 --> 01:16:25.000
But. of course.
I never taught you that one.

1364
01:16:25.583 --> 01:16:26.458
Shoot.

1365
01:16:28.000 --> 01:16:29.166
(SIGHS)

1366
01:16:29.167 --> 01:16:32.750
Now. I just want to put
your mind at ease. okay?

1367
01:16:33.583 --> 01:16:36.875
The toxins from
the <i>Hapalochlaena lunulata</i>

1368
01:16:37.500 --> 01:16:38.792
aren't gonna kill you.

1369
01:16:39.792 --> 01:16:42.291
And I promise
they will wear off.

1370
01:16:42.292 --> 01:16:44.792
But right now. you won't be able
to move or feel anything.

1371
01:16:45.500 --> 01:16:47.541
And trust me...
(SIGHS)

1372
01:16:47.542 --> 01:16:49.167
...I think you want it that way.

1373
01:16:50.292 --> 01:16:51.500
Ooh.

1374
01:17:00.042 --> 01:17:01.250
(EXHALES SHARPLY)

1375
01:17:02.292 --> 01:17:03.542
Where was I?

1376
01:17:04.250 --> 01:17:09.207
So. when I was a little girl.
we had this dog.

1377
01:17:09.208 --> 01:17:10.791
BRADLEY: (GRUNTS)

1378
01:17:10.792 --> 01:17:13.957
Very. very naughty dog.
So disobedient.

1379
01:17:13.958 --> 01:17:17.000
- (WHIMPERS)
- Always running away.

1380
01:17:18.833 --> 01:17:19.666
(GRUNTS)

1381
01:17:19.667 --> 01:17:23.666
And my dad said.
"It's not his fault.

1382
01:17:23.667 --> 01:17:26.166
(CHUCKLES)
He just..."

1383
01:17:26.167 --> 01:17:27.542
(GRUNTS)

1384
01:17:28.583 --> 01:17:31.333
(SIGHS)
"...needs to be fixed."

1385
01:17:37.208 --> 01:17:38.250
Now...

1386
01:17:39.500 --> 01:17:42.083
- it's actually quite a simple...
- (METAL SCRAPES)

1387
01:17:43.333 --> 01:17:44.583
...medical procedure.

1388
01:17:44.958 --> 01:17:48.167
They used to do it
all the time to Egyptian slaves.

1389
01:17:48.750 --> 01:17:51.542
Made them more. um. obedient.

1390
01:17:52.250 --> 01:17:54.083
- Compliant.
- (WHIMPERS)

1391
01:17:56.833 --> 01:17:57.833
(WHISPERS) Okay.

1392
01:18:00.667 --> 01:18:02.125
No help is coming.

1393
01:18:03.750 --> 01:18:05.833
This is the way things are now.

1394
01:18:06.250 --> 01:18:08.458
And you need
to just accept that.

1395
01:18:09.917 --> 01:18:11.500
You are stuck.

1396
01:18:12.375 --> 01:18:13.458
No power.

1397
01:18:13.917 --> 01:18:15.833
Low end of the totem pole.

1398
01:18:17.125 --> 01:18:19.208
With some asshole boss.

1399
01:18:19.958 --> 01:18:21.417
Just like I was.

1400
01:18:22.417 --> 01:18:24.124
Although. I'm betting...

1401
01:18:24.125 --> 01:18:27.458
I am a much nicer boss
than you ever would have been.

1402
01:18:29.708 --> 01:18:32.875
(GASPS)
Except for maybe this part.

1403
01:18:35.625 --> 01:18:36.583
Ready?

1404
01:18:38.417 --> 01:18:40.250
(MUFFLED WHINING)

1405
01:18:41.083 --> 01:18:43.416
- (GASPS)
- (SQUELCHING)

1406
01:18:43.417 --> 01:18:44.791
- Okay.
- (MUFFLED YELP)

1407
01:18:44.792 --> 01:18:46.374
Now. now. don't be a baby.

1408
01:18:46.375 --> 01:18:47.958
You're not gonna miss
this stuff.

1409
01:18:49.042 --> 01:18:51.375
- (KNIFE CLINKS)
- (SUSTAINED YELP)

1410
01:18:51.875 --> 01:18:53.457
(YELPS)

1411
01:18:53.458 --> 01:18:56.749
- (KNIFE SLICING)
- (MUFFLED WAILING)

1412
01:18:56.750 --> 01:18:58.582
- (WAILS)
- Ooh!

1413
01:18:58.583 --> 01:19:00.874
(MUFFLED WAILING)

1414
01:19:00.875 --> 01:19:02.749
(CHUCKLES)
We got a bleeder here.

1415
01:19:02.750 --> 01:19:04.874
- (YELPS)
- (BRIGHTLY) A lot of blood.

1416
01:19:04.875 --> 01:19:06.541
- (GROANING)
- (CHUCKLING) Wow.

1417
01:19:06.542 --> 01:19:10.000
(GROANING)

1418
01:19:10.792 --> 01:19:12.000
Oh.

1419
01:19:13.000 --> 01:19:14.417
(SIGHS)

1420
01:19:16.125 --> 01:19:17.500
(MUFFLED CRY)

1421
01:19:18.292 --> 01:19:20.375
- It's okay. It's just a rat.
- (GROANS)

1422
01:19:21.250 --> 01:19:22.542
- (GROANS)
- (RAT SPLATTERS)

1423
01:19:25.708 --> 01:19:27.667
Next time it won't be a rat.

1424
01:19:29.875 --> 01:19:33.667
So. don't ever mistake
my kindness for weakness.

1425
01:19:34.833 --> 01:19:40.750
(GRUNTING)

1426
01:19:48.667 --> 01:19:49.833
Hey. there!

1427
01:19:50.917 --> 01:19:52.250
How goes it?

1428
01:19:55.708 --> 01:19:58.042
Barely talked in two days.
you Gloomy Gus.

1429
01:20:02.167 --> 01:20:04.458
Would it kill you
to give me a little smile?

1430
01:20:12.958 --> 01:20:14.958
Mmm. There it is.

1431
01:20:16.125 --> 01:20:18.000
Tell you what I'm gonna do
to cheer you up.

1432
01:20:18.833 --> 01:20:20.292
I'm gonna go find...

1433
01:20:21.208 --> 01:20:24.499
the juiciest. most beautiful
fruits on this whole island

1434
01:20:24.500 --> 01:20:26.083
and make you a little treat.

1435
01:20:31.625 --> 01:20:33.499
Such a sourpuss.

1436
01:20:33.500 --> 01:20:36.499
Make him a little fire.
and he's gonna come around.

1437
01:20:36.500 --> 01:20:38.958
(ENGINE HUMMING)

1438
01:20:44.500 --> 01:20:47.667
(GASPS)

1439
01:20:49.875 --> 01:20:52.166
ZURI: Hello? Hello?

1440
01:20:52.167 --> 01:20:53.292
Shit.

1441
01:20:55.667 --> 01:20:57.832
Linda! It's me.

1442
01:20:57.833 --> 01:21:00.832
(RAPIDLY) Shit. shit.
shit. shit. shit. shit...

1443
01:21:00.833 --> 01:21:04.874
Oh. my God! We found her!
I did it. I can't believe it.

1444
01:21:04.875 --> 01:21:06.125
Hey.

1445
01:21:07.458 --> 01:21:08.749
- Hey.
- No. no. no.

1446
01:21:08.750 --> 01:21:09.749
(EXAGGERATED GIGGLE)

1447
01:21:09.750 --> 01:21:11.624
- Come here!
- (GIGGLE CONTINUES)

1448
01:21:11.625 --> 01:21:12.957
ZURI: Oh. my God.

1449
01:21:12.958 --> 01:21:15.083
Hi. Hello.

1450
01:21:16.458 --> 01:21:18.416
Is he alive? Is he here?

1451
01:21:18.417 --> 01:21:19.416
How on earth?

1452
01:21:19.417 --> 01:21:21.707
Bradley. is he-- is he here?

1453
01:21:21.708 --> 01:21:22.749
- Yes.
- He is?

1454
01:21:22.750 --> 01:21:24.416
- Yes. he's here.
- Oh. my God.

1455
01:21:24.417 --> 01:21:26.083
- He is here.
- He's alive!

1456
01:21:27.125 --> 01:21:28.999
Even when they called off
the search in this area.

1457
01:21:29.000 --> 01:21:30.457
I never gave up.

1458
01:21:30.458 --> 01:21:32.791
- I couldn't give up.
- That's amazing.

1459
01:21:32.792 --> 01:21:35.124
I hired my own boat.
I did my own search.

1460
01:21:35.125 --> 01:21:37.416
Is he okay? Is he hurt? Is he...

1461
01:21:37.417 --> 01:21:38.708
He's fine.

1462
01:21:39.583 --> 01:21:42.416
- He's so good. He's great.
- Great.

1463
01:21:42.417 --> 01:21:44.249
I can't believe
this is happening.

1464
01:21:44.250 --> 01:21:46.082
- I know.
- (CACKLES)

1465
01:21:46.083 --> 01:21:47.999
Please. can you take me to him?
Right now?

1466
01:21:48.000 --> 01:21:50.124
- I need to see him. Please.
- He's. um...

1467
01:21:50.125 --> 01:21:51.124
Is he just down here?

1468
01:21:51.125 --> 01:21:52.249
- Yes. he's out here.
- Yeah? He is?

1469
01:21:52.250 --> 01:21:53.624
No. no. no.

1470
01:21:53.625 --> 01:21:54.916
- He's not over there.
- Bradley. I'm here!

1471
01:21:54.917 --> 01:21:56.791
- Um--
- Bradley. where are you?

1472
01:21:56.792 --> 01:21:58.250
MAN: Should we follow you?

1473
01:21:59.333 --> 01:22:00.417
This way?

1474
01:22:02.083 --> 01:22:03.041
(SIGHS)

1475
01:22:03.042 --> 01:22:04.458
Should we follow you?

1476
01:22:04.750 --> 01:22:05.875
Uh...

1477
01:22:06.458 --> 01:22:09.332
- I just need to get my stuff.
- You're not gonna need this.

1478
01:22:09.333 --> 01:22:10.666
- (SMACKS)
- Ow.

1479
01:22:10.667 --> 01:22:13.417
- Sorry. Sorry. I just...
- You like mango. right?

1480
01:22:13.958 --> 01:22:14.874
Yeah. I worked really hard.

1481
01:22:14.875 --> 01:22:16.792
We got lots of food on the boat.

1482
01:22:18.917 --> 01:22:19.875
Oh. yum.

1483
01:22:20.917 --> 01:22:21.917
Yum. yum. yum.

1484
01:22:22.458 --> 01:22:23.583
Lead the way.

1485
01:22:24.250 --> 01:22:27.292
So. is it just the two of you?

1486
01:22:28.167 --> 01:22:30.582
Or is there a whole search party
waiting for us?

1487
01:22:30.583 --> 01:22:31.708
MAN: Just us.

1488
01:22:32.375 --> 01:22:35.791
But there will be many people
happy to hear you two are alive.

1489
01:22:35.792 --> 01:22:36.874
Once I radio back.

1490
01:22:36.875 --> 01:22:39.208
You'll be back in your own bed
in no time.

1491
01:22:39.917 --> 01:22:41.875
There's a shortcut
just ahead here.

1492
01:22:52.208 --> 01:22:54.957
ZURI: I bet you can't wait
to return to your life.

1493
01:22:54.958 --> 01:22:58.499
Your job. your family.
your friends.

1494
01:22:58.500 --> 01:23:00.292
(MAN SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY)

1495
01:23:23.333 --> 01:23:25.542
Uh. shoelace.

1496
01:23:26.417 --> 01:23:27.375
Okay.

1497
01:23:27.708 --> 01:23:30.582
- Just follow the trail.
- ZURI: Yeah.

1498
01:23:30.583 --> 01:23:32.167
I'm right behind you.

1499
01:23:42.417 --> 01:23:45.792
(SLOWED BREATHING)

1500
01:23:51.542 --> 01:23:53.666
(SCREAMS)

1501
01:23:53.667 --> 01:23:55.624
Zuri! Zuri! Zuri! Come on!

1502
01:23:55.625 --> 01:23:58.582
- ZURI: (GRUNTING)
- Grab my hand. Hey. Come on!

1503
01:23:58.583 --> 01:24:01.166
I got you. I got you.
You can do it. You can do it.

1504
01:24:01.167 --> 01:24:02.874
Help me! Help me!

1505
01:24:02.875 --> 01:24:04.624
- ZURI: (GROANS)
- Come on. Come on.

1506
01:24:04.625 --> 01:24:05.957
I got you!

1507
01:24:05.958 --> 01:24:07.249
- Zuri! Come on.
- ZURI: Linda. help us!

1508
01:24:07.250 --> 01:24:09.332
I got you. You can do it.
You can do it.

1509
01:24:09.333 --> 01:24:10.999
I got you. You can do it.

1510
01:24:11.000 --> 01:24:12.666
Man: (GROANING)

1511
01:24:12.667 --> 01:24:14.041
Help me!

1512
01:24:14.042 --> 01:24:15.292
- Linda!
- Linda!

1513
01:24:15.750 --> 01:24:17.124
MAN: Help us!

1514
01:24:17.125 --> 01:24:19.875
ZURI: Linda!

1515
01:24:31.375 --> 01:24:32.583
Dinner.

1516
01:24:34.042 --> 01:24:35.042
Yep.

1517
01:24:38.750 --> 01:24:40.125
(SIGHS)

1518
01:25:17.833 --> 01:25:20.708
(RAIN PATTERING)

1519
01:25:26.667 --> 01:25:29.000
Saw some fresh boar tracks
earlier today.

1520
01:25:30.333 --> 01:25:32.000
We haven't had protein
in awhile.

1521
01:25:33.542 --> 01:25:35.542
Maybe when it clears up
we should go hunting.

1522
01:25:39.333 --> 01:25:40.958
I'm taking a sick day.

1523
01:25:44.167 --> 01:25:45.583
Can't do it on my own.

1524
01:26:19.292 --> 01:26:22.833
(SIGHS)

1525
01:26:28.542 --> 01:26:30.583
ZURI: (DISTANTLY) Linda!

1526
01:26:59.500 --> 01:27:02.917
(GROANS)

1527
01:27:06.292 --> 01:27:08.875
(GASPING)

1528
01:27:18.000 --> 01:27:21.792
(STRAINED GROANS)

1529
01:27:23.792 --> 01:27:26.750
(GASPING)

1530
01:27:33.208 --> 01:27:34.458
(GRUNTING FEEBLY)

1531
01:27:36.792 --> 01:27:38.333
(WAILING) Linda.

1532
01:27:39.708 --> 01:27:41.792
Linda!

1533
01:27:43.167 --> 01:27:45.582
You tried to kill me.

1534
01:27:45.583 --> 01:27:47.417
- No.
- Why?

1535
01:27:48.417 --> 01:27:49.625
(CRYING) Why?

1536
01:27:50.292 --> 01:27:51.833
Why'd you do it?

1537
01:27:53.458 --> 01:27:56.999
(GROANS) Why?
(CRYING)

1538
01:27:57.000 --> 01:27:58.999
Why'd you have to come?

1539
01:27:59.000 --> 01:28:00.291
I'm gonna tell Bradley
everything.

1540
01:28:00.292 --> 01:28:01.207
No.

1541
01:28:01.208 --> 01:28:02.749
- You're a murderer.
- No.

1542
01:28:02.750 --> 01:28:04.124
- You are!
- (SCREAMS)

1543
01:28:04.125 --> 01:28:06.208
(GRUNTING)

1544
01:28:08.750 --> 01:28:09.917
(GASPS)

1545
01:28:15.458 --> 01:28:16.666
(ROARS)

1546
01:28:16.667 --> 01:28:18.458
(SCREAMS)

1547
